data.description:
MUSTANG Schools!  STORM SHELTER!   - MUSTANG SCHOOLS ! Wonderful home in the Sycamore Creek Addition.  Built by Home Creations this home boast of 1561 SF, MASTER IN LAW PLAN with 3 Bedrooms, 2 full baths, 2 car garage, Central Heat and Air, includes a FLAT SAFE STORM SHELTER built in garage floor. 

Great living room with magnificent hall entrance. Kitchen is open & bright with PANTRY ,breakfast bar & tons of storage. CROWN MOLDING, gas log fireplace, double vanity & garden tub, separate shower in master, faux blinds, security system & established landscape.  Ceramic tile in all the important places.  Very, Very Clean. Easy I40 and Kilpatrick Turnpike access.

Call or text Ralph 405-585-1066 for more information or to schedule a showing.

(RLNE2510283)
